videos.description: Shakayla Thomas makes the fast-break layup to give Florida State an early lead over Connecticut.
videos.headline: Thomas' fast-break layup gives Florida State early lead
Florida State turns defense into offense off an Ivey Slaughter steal

videos.description: Natalie Butler makes a nice move in the post on her way to a layup to increase Connecticut's lead over Florida State.
videos.headline: Natalie Butler shakes her defender for the bucket

videos.description: Brittany Brown steals the ball away and takes it the other way for a bucket plus the foul to increase Florida State's lead over Connecticut.
videos.headline: Brittany Brown's steal leads to another bucket for FSU

videos.description: Q3 (2:12) FSU Imani Wright made Layup.
videos.headline: Imani Wright gets the steal and converts it into two points at the other end

videos.description: Saniya Chong cuts through the Florida State defense to give Connecticut a lead.
videos.headline: Chong cuts through the FSU defense for the layup

videos.description: Florida State misses the shot and Connecticut takes it the other way, leading to Saniya Chong shooting a three-pointer.
videos.headline: Saniya Chong hits a three for Connecticut

videos.description: Q4 (1:01) CONN Saniya Chong made Layup.
videos.headline: Saniya Chong weaves through the defense to give UConn a 4-point lead with a minute remaining

videos.description: Q4 (0:46) FSU Imani Wright made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Chatrice White.
videos.headline: Florida State 3-Pointer cuts the UConn lead to 1 in the final minute of the game

videos.description: Q4 (0:13) CONN Foul on Kia Nurse.
videos.headline: UConn gets called for a foul on 3-point attempt with a 3-point lead with under 15 seconds left in the game
UConn defense gets a block with under 10 seconds left to preserve the lead

videos.description: Down by two in the closing seconds of the fourth quarter, Brittany Brown tries to win it for Florida State with a 3-pointer, but it's no good, giving Connecticut a 78-76 win.
videos.headline: FSU's failed three gives UConn a close win
